BUTTONS

BOOLEANS
A - sample intake FSM (DONE) / wall grab FSM
B - sample transfer FSM (DONE) / raise specimen FSM
Y - sample outtake FSM (DONE) / score specimen FSM
X - slow mode
rightBumper - drive towards basket
leftBumper - specimen mode
dLeft - move intake slides in (DONE)
dRight - move intake slides out (DONE)
dUp - claw open/close (DONE)
dDown - field centric mode
leftStickButton - low basket mode
rightStickButton - vertical slide manual mode (DONE)
back button - reset robot
start button - reset encoders

DOUBLES
rightTrigger - intake spin in (DONE) / vertical slides up (DONE)
leftTrigger - intake spin out (DONE) / vertical slides down (DONE)
leftStickX - strafe
leftStickY - forward/back
rightStickX - spin
rightStickY - spin (in field centric)
touchPadX -
touchPadY -


